description:
The ESL Pro League Championship 2024 for Counter-strike in is scheduled to conclude on September 22, 2024. You can find more information about that tournament here: https://pro.eslgaming.com/csgo/proleague/standings/

This market will resolve to "G2" if G2 Esports advances in the tournament after their match against Team Liquid scheduled for September 20. This market will resolve to "Liquid" if Team Liquid advances after their match against G2 Esports.

If for any reason neither team advances, or their match is postponed after September 22, 2024, 11:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market is official information provided directly from ESL (e.g. pro.eslgaming.com) and official footage of the tournament, however other credible reporting may be used.
